・列に別名をつける
select name as 名前, price as 価格 from products;
（asは省略可）

・税込価格表示
select
	name as 名前,
	price as 価格,
  price * 1.08 as 税込価格　←　計算できる
from
	products;

・条件検索(where句)
select name 名前, price 価格 from products where price >= 9800;

